### Create React Frontend Intern job
POST http://localhost:8082/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "React Frontend Intern",
  "company": "StartupXYZ",
  "description": "Build and maintain React components for our web application",
  "stipend": "12000",
  "location": "Mumbai"
}

